        <p>Someone recently asked for my card at an event - so here's my digital version!</p>
        
        <p>I've been folk dancing for just over a year and started calling with Bristol University Folk Society Ceilidhs. Now, I'm keen to expand into Contra calling.</p>
        
        <p>As a newer caller, I bring fresh energy and a stand-up comedy background to keep things lively. I use non-gendered calling and focus on making everyone, especially newcomers, feel welcome and comfortable on the dance floor.</p>
        
        <p>I'm eager to gain more experience and would be delighted to call at your event. If you have any open caller slots, please get in touch!</p>
        
